message: "If you use this code, please cite it as below."
type: software
title: "DPADD-ES: Component-Aware Separation-Enhanced Audio Deepfake Detection for ESDD2"
authors:
  - family-names: Iragena
    given-names: Yves Alain
    email: iragena@cua.edu
    affiliation: "Multimodal AI Lab (MAIL), The Catholic University of America"
